verbose_text: Western blotting verified that the expression levels of the representative synaptic associated proteins, Syn1 and Snap25, were significantly reduced in the cortex of VD model rats compared with the control group, and were markedly increased in the cortex of miR-134-5p antagomir rats compared with VD model rats (XREF_FIG).
evidence: levels of the representative synaptic-associated proteins, Syn1
